ENTRY       EC 1.1.1.50                 Enzyme
NAME        3alpha-hydroxysteroid 3-dehydrogenase (Si-specific);
            hydroxyprostaglandin dehydrogenase;
            3alpha-hydroxysteroid oxidoreductase;
            sterognost 3alpha;
            3alpha-hydroxysteroid dehydrogenase (B-specific);
