            3alpha-hydroxysteroid:NAD(P)+ 3-oxidoreductase (B-specific)
CLASS       Oxidoreductases;
            Acting on the CH-OH group of donors;
            With NAD+ or NADP+ as acceptor
SYSNAME     3alpha-hydroxysteroid:NAD(P)+ 3-oxidoreductase (Si-specific)
REACTION    a 3alpha-hydroxysteroid + NAD(P)+ = a 3-oxosteroid + NAD(P)H + H+ [RN:R10422 R10423]
ALL_REAC    R10422 > R02476 R04309 R04818 R04824 R04829 R04832 R04835 R04837 R04842 R04845;
