PRODUCT     3-oxosteroid [CPD:C01876];
            NADH [CPD:C00004];
            NADPH [CPD:C00005];
            H+ [CPD:C00080]
COMMENT     The enzyme acts on androsterone and other 3alpha-hydroxysteroids and on 9-, 11- and 15-hydroxyprostaglandin. Si-specific with respect to NAD+ or NADP+. cf. EC 1.1.1.213, 3alpha-hydroxysteroid 3-dehydrogenase (Re-specific).
